OL,3,CMother found dead alongside disabled
OL,4,Cdaughter refused help, inquest hears
OL,6,FAn inquest has heard how a mother in
OL,7,FNottingham, found dead at home with
OL,8,Fher disabled daughter, repeatedly
OL,9,Frefused help from local services.
OL,11,FThe bodies of Alphonsine Djiako Leuga,
OL,12,F47, and Loraine Choulla, 18, were
OL,13,Fdiscovered last May at their council
OL,14,Fhome in Radford.
OL,16,FIt's thought they could have been dead
OL,17,Ffor months.
