OL,3,CMother found dead alongside disabled
OL,4,Cdaughter refused help, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe began attending a special
OL,7,Feducational needs school, but in
OL,8,FAutumn 2021 Ms Leuga stopped sending
OL,9,Fher to school, the inquest heard.
OL,11,FAttempts to carry out vital
OL,12,Fmaintenance works on the property were
OL,13,Fstopped by Ms Leuga and the court
OL,14,Fheard how in April 2023 the gas supply
OL,15,Fwas turned off after workers were
OL,16,Fdenied access to the house to carry
OL,17,Fout an annual safety check.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
