OL,3,CMother found dead alongside disabled
OL,4,Cdaughter refused help, inquest hears
OL,6,FOn another occasion, Ms Leuga told
OL,7,Fsocial workers she didn't trust them
OL,8,Fand she was concerned they would take
OL,9,Fher daughter away.
OL,11,FHer last contact with the authorities
OL,12,Fwas when she dialled 999 asking for
OL,13,Fhelp, but an ambulance was never sent.
OL,15,FEast Midlands Ambulance Service's head
OL,16,Fof patient safety, Susan Jevons, said
OL,17,Fthere had been "a missed opportunity
OL,18,Ffor an ambulance to attend Alphonsine
OL,19,Fwhen she requested one".
