OL,3,CMother found dead alongside disabled
OL,4,Cdaughter refused help, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest heard that Ms Leuga
OL,7,Fsuffered from sickle cell anaemia and
OL,8,Fdied from pneumonia. Miss Choulla's
OL,9,Fcause of death is as yet unknown.
OL,11,FA statement by Ms Leuga's eldest
OL,12,Fdaughter, Elvira Choulla, was also
OL,13,Fread out at the inquest.
OL,15,FShe said she had moved in with her
OL,16,Fmother and younger sister in 2019, but
OL,17,Fmoved out to live independently three
OL,18,Fyears later.
