OL,3,CMother found dead alongside disabled
OL,4,Cdaughter refused help, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest heard she would often
OL,7,Fvisit them, but that her relationship
OL,8,Fwith her mother deteriorated to the
OL,9,Fpoint that the visits almost entirely
OL,10,Fstopped.
OL,12,FThe next time she heard any news about
OL,13,Fthem was when police told her they had
OL,14,Fpassed away, the inquest heard.
OL,16,FElvira Choulla described Loraine as a
OL,17,F"friendly and bubbly girl".
OL,19,FShe added: "She loved being around
OL,20,Fpeople and I never saw her sad. I
OL,21,Floved her and she loved me back."
